      "writtenOn": "2019-05-02T17:43:40Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "It seems like we will want a Swarming cache for gopath.\n\nIf not, it seems like this should be in a tmp dir; usually dirs under start_dir are for CIPD packages and isolated inputs and outputs.\n\nAlso in infra/bots/task_drivers/infra_tests/infra_tests.go.",
